Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Daihaseisai underway, Academy City is full of activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}Using that opportunity, a trade for "Stab Sword", a spiritual weapon capable of killing Saints in one blow, is taking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the courier is Oriana Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just happened to stumble across someone who seems to be her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:25.36,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(670,849)\pos(816,484)}#09 Route Disturb\NTrace Sealer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the spot where Oriana may make the trade—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just shook hands with someone, and my Imagine Breaker destroyed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I destroyed, but she doesn't seem to be a student...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she carrying anything big?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's carrying what looks to be a display board.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you right now, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm following her at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you my GPS coordinates, so use that to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She noticed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... she's that blonde woman wearing work clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two sure are pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agreed not to use my magic while in town, but I can't underestimate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like her path has changed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she change her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a maintenance area for automatic buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.83,0:02:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think this is some pretty awesome team play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assigning specific roles allows us to understand and act better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, go do your part!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I said give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl, set up your rune cards here and stay on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the courier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be safer for you to just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll be safer to just stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my safety, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are just decoys to buy time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll escape if you try to take them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counting on me for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Route Disturb", Oriana Thomson, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This spell is "All-Direction Rational Formation".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this to discover Oriana's current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it bad for you to use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll need some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Convey the wind; not the air, but your will here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Convey the wind; not the air, but your will here"... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit Stiyl's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like an anti-tracking defense spell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, there aren't any traces of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that she cast an automatic counterattack spell that responds to Stiyl's unique magical profile.{lit: mana}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean Stiyl can't use magic against Oriana anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that's a pretty annoying trick she put together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Analyzing my vitality from a single piece of flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did she reverse calculate with ease, but she even counterattacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Route Disturb lives up to her reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Route Disturb?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Oriana Thomson's magic name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I seem to remember seeing this inhuman "auto-processing" method before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she'd have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's it's true, she's not just a magician, but a sorcerer, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By compacting magical knowledge into a container,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the knowledge itself will result in a type of magical formation regardless of the container's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An original grimoire copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for her to create a grimoire specifically for the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be an original, but it's still a rough copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only has limited effects, and will self-destruct quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could call it a "Shorthand."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with destroying the automatic counterattack spell so that Stiyl can use magic again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While we do that, there's a possibility she'll escape beyond our search range...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'd take the time to set up a counterattack spell if she knew she could escape so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use some magic. I don't care what kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Divining Circle Formation."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a magical formation that has yet to be used and does not require the use of one's mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}It responds to the energy of a magical counterattack spell and calculates the direction and distance of the spell's origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use that once again, Stiyl will—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once" again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to do this as many times as it takes to discover the location of the Shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me remind you of something you seem to have forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle with lives on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countries, or even the world could collapse, depending on the outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lack resolve, Kamijou Touma.{lit: being too close}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it can put an end to this, then it's worth the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, find the location of the counterattack spell no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also make sure Index can carry on living like she has in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd request that as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It annoys me that you're here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she becomes unhappy as a result of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll all be your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to change into this and surprise Touma, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he just ran off somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so sad, Sister-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kamijou-chan had a good reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kamijou Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappearing right when I take my eyes off him, sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing outside school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's just a little dizzy, we can use a stimulus like spice powder to bring her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! It's fine, Fukiyose-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Touma have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Divining Circle Formation" is responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get me a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have that GPS map on your cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that would put this around—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have go this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Stiyl have to injure himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a professional magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He at least has some level of resistance against magical attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Divining Circle Formation" responds to incoming magic attacks and shows me its direction and distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I could break out something so convenient without using magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were able to use magic more effectively, Stiyl wouldn't have ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, and you can curse me all you want for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still going to find the Shorthand and destroy it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will definitely capture Oriana and crush this Stab Sword transaction with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what's 302 meters northwest of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shorthand should be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A middle school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:59.64,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}10 minutes until the Middle School Ball-Toss Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the competition grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spectators and press are already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be sneaky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just leave it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to slip in as contestants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're high schoolers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can sneak into a middle school competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That counterattack spell may endanger other people too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what the most basic magic ritual in the world is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility that an ordinary person may activate the counterattack spell just by touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, it'll be very dangerous for them due to their lack of magical resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kami-yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to deal with the counterattack spell before we have casualties to deal with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the contest that's about to start, but do we have to participate looking like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are cameras too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have spare PE clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the clubroom though...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hurry up and go change then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the rules, so just let me check your IDs first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wipe your hand before using it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, whatever. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't let you join if you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really going to sneak in looking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they must have spare clothes in the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next contest will be the Ball Toss
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between 200 students from Minamizawa Middle School and 20 students from Tokiwadai Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can smell the dread from their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are {\i1}you{\i0} doing there?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Tokiwadai Middle School?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're full of powerful espers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just watch out for flying balls, Kami-yan.{FLYING BALLSSSSS}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming the Shorthand was cast here somewhere, where would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think those baskets are the most suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're likely to have been borrowed from somewhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she may have cast it on one of them before they were brought in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check out each of those poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn will come once we find the Shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.25,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}Daihaseisai Administration Station
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get set...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.91,0:15:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get in there, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan! This isn't it either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want me to take the punishment {\i1}that{\i0}  badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in danger, so I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Misaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Misaka, I'll tell you everything later...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain that firs—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet and come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be perfectly fine even without you coming to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you mean, "tell me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about me so much over a little contest like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, saying weird things like that out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't surprise me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, could you not be feeling well, Misaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you have a fever—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sick or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.13,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}Nogi Middle School Equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran here to see what the fuss was, and I find you here?{girls in this series have some penchant for randomly holding onto poles?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm calling an end to this match!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, touch Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her body won't be able to take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now, Oriana Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is how you're going to do things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to drag innocent people into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And feel absolutely nothing as you watch it all happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will take that damn illusion of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and completely destroy it with this fist of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.92,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as for Stiyl and Tsuchimikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the cause of this conflict is the Stab Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will destroy it, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, this epic will begin!
